relation: Going to different games and joining clubs are very fun to do.
The food at the school is very good and there are healthy options to choose from.
I've never lived on campus. That's one thing I would like to do though. :)
The academic rigor is good. I've always loved a challenge when it came to my schoolwork.
Go to the campus just to get a feel. Always study, but don't overload yourself.
I love the opportunities available at this school. There are a wide variety of majors to choose from. The instructors are always there to help when we as students need them.

textAfterTable: Academic Rigor The professors are really great here. However though, they do not push you to your limits like some professors are known to. This is a much rather 'easier' college. Tips for prospective students 2 Bedroom Suites have bigger rooms but no living room 4 Bedroom Suites have smaller rooms but with living room So if you're a people person and like to hangout, I recommend the 4 bedroom suite. In three sentences South Georiga College is a great place to start going to college right out of high school. It is not a huge jump to a higher university but more like a stepping stone to feel the atmosphere for the college life. I would recommend it for those looking to start their college lives nice and easy while saving money at the same time.
